commentTextItems.html: on the backfoot, cut away to point that is it. the match is over. India win by 8 wickets

commentPostTextItems.html: Blames playing 3 matches in 5 days with jet lag in between
Could have easily been Chopra or Robin Singh
Yet another man of the match award for Ganguly at Toronto
We will be back again tomorrow with the hope that the match will be played better than today

commentTextItems.html: outside the off, cut away to third man
